      "content": "it's not just feeling lost tho. it feels like there’s actually nothing there. no meaning, no purpose, no grand design. just entropy and then nothingness. people try to tell me things get better or there's some higher purpose, but that's just a lie to keep us from panicking. it's just easier to accept that there's nothing to look forward to.",
